This paper deals with the problem of handwritten numeral recognition using a Multi Layer Perceptron (MLP) based classifier. This falls under the domain of Computer Vision (cs.CV) as it involves image processing and pattern recognition. The use of MLP also suggests that it falls under the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of OCR (Optical Character Recognition) which is a common application of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL). Therefore, the likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CL, in that order.
